abstract: Tampa Bay Buccaneers quarterback Jameis Winston files defamation suit against Erica Kinsman, who is accusing him of rape.
lead_paragraph: Winston filed counterclaims against the woman who has accused him of rape, responding to her lawsuit Friday in federal court in Orlando, Fla.

headline.main: Jameis Winston Files Countersuit Against Accuser
